sketch.compiler.ast.core

Class Package

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.Package

  • public class Package
extends FENode
    Similar to a namespace in C++, contains private fields (global variables local to the package), structures and functions. A Package may or may not have a name; if there is no name, this is an anonymous package. It also has a list of global variable declarations (currently they are called global field declaration and are all FieldDecl nodes), a list of function declarations (as Function objects), and a list of TypeStruct definitions.
    Version:
